  <!-- EN: QingMing tree -->
  <RI_Tree_QingMing.label>青冥树</RI_Tree_QingMing.label>
  <!-- EN: The blue sky shakes the smoke tree, the sky crosses the negative stone.\n\nQingMing tree has the ability to gather Qi, the trunk is strong, the branches and leaves are lush, and the precious heartwood can be harvested for the production of QingMing jade wine. It is said that this tree comes from an ancient five-element Initial approach, the wood element, which they created to expand the population of cultivators. -->
  <RI_Tree_QingMing.description>青冥摇烟树，穹跨负天石。\n\n青冥树，有通天聚灵之能，树干粗壮，枝叶繁茂，采伐可得宝贵心材青冥髓，用于制作青玉仙露。据说这种树来自于一支古老的五行法门——木行，是他们将这种树创造了出来，用于扩大修炼者的人口。</RI_Tree_QingMing.description>
  
